title: Green Ginger Noodle House
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Juice bar, Take-out, Asian, Fusion
description: Contemporary cafe and vintage store in a shabby chic space - look for the blue color exterior. Has a meditative garden in the  back. The food is modern Asian. Recycles and uses minimized reusable packaging, uses local produce. Confirmed open, May 2016.
